                          '<h3>1. Core logic of pediatric cancer</h3>\n'
                          '<p>The main difference between pediatric cancer and adult oncology is that cure rates are '
                          'often high, but the cost of late toxicity is also high.</p>\n'
                          '<p>The goal of pediatric RT is not simply to deliver enough dose. The goal is '
