                          '      <tr><td>Peritoneal metastases/malignant ascites</td><td>24 Gy at 1.5 '
                          'Gy/fraction</td><td>Whole abdomen</td></tr>\n'
                          '    </tbody>\n'
                          '  </table>\n'
                          '</div>\n'
                          '<p>Postoperative RT indications include R1 resection, &lt;90% necrosis, and tumor '
                          'spill.</p>\n'
                          '<h3>6. Evidence</h3>\n'
                          '<p>AEWS1031 tested interval-compressed VDC/IE versus adding topotecan-containing VTC within '
